title: Stake CAKE tokens to earn pCWS tokens!
body:
# The Syrup Pool:
Total Tokens: 7,500 pCWS
Distribution duration: 60 days
Start block: 5954000 (March 24th 3PM SGT)
Finish block: 7682000 (May 23rd 3PM SGT)
Token rewards per block: 0.00434 pCWS


# The Farm:
In order to host the pCWS Syrup Pool, we will need to provide a pCWS-BNB farm that will have 2x CAKE rewards for the first 48 hours and then 1x CAKE rewards after that. 


# The Vote:
As usual, it needs to be approved via a vote.

Why do we need a vote? Since it dilutes rewards, the chefs want BSC’s greatest community to make the decision themselves.
author: 0x6eaf1b33b8672c5dc40aB8f4bA3A0111723126c7
